Day 68: Set Up Jenkins Server

Date: November 5, 2025
Overview
Installed and configured Jenkins automation server.
Key Concepts Learned

Jenkins installation methods
Initial admin password retrieval
Basic Jenkins architecture
Plugin ecosystem

Commands Used
bashsudo wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/jenkins.repo https://pkg.jenkins.io/redhat-stable/jenkins.repo
sudo rpm --import https://pkg.jenkins.io/redhat-stable/jenkins.io.key
sudo yum install jenkins java-11-openjdk
sudo systemctl start jenkins
sudo cat /var/lib/jenkins/secrets/initialAdminPassword

Challenges Faced
Java version compatibility and firewall configuration. Port 8080 needed to be opened!
